### Get all inhabitants for authenticated user
GET {{baseUrl}}/inhabitants
Authorization: {{token}}

### Get specific inhabitant by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/inhabitants/1
Authorization: {{token}}

### Get inhabitants by aquarium ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/inhabitants?aquariumId=1
Authorization: {{token}}

### Create new fish inhabitant
POST {{baseUrl}}/inhabitants
Authorization: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Nemo",
  "species": "Clownfish",
  "color": "Orange and White",
